# Vendor packages – credits and licenses

exarp-go vendors Go dependencies in `vendor/`. The original **exarp** project maintained a third-party notices / credits file; this document continues that practice and lists each vendored package with its license for attribution and compliance.

**How to regenerate:** run `make vendor-licenses` (or `./scripts/vendor_licenses.sh` from repo root).

For duplication checks and improvement ideas (e.g. spf13/cast, rate limiter), see [VENDOR_USAGE_AND_IMPROVEMENTS.md](VENDOR_USAGE_AND_IMPROVEMENTS.md).
